3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227694%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zavalivskyi%20Graphite%20Plant%20in%20Ukraine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6814997f3fe8d3928364b8f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225132%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Zavalivskyi%20graphite%20plant%20in%20Ukraine.%20The%20war-torn%20country%20has%20signed%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20US%20to%20grant%20American%20firms%20access%20to%20critical%20minerals.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US-Ukraine%20minerals%20deal%20grants%20US%20firms%20access%20to%20critical%20resources%20like%20graphite%20and%20lithium.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20experts%20warn%20that%20commercial%20opportunities%20are%20limited%2C%20and%20certainly%20won't%20be%20immediate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEven%20if%20Ukraine%20could%20fast-track%20approvals%2C%20the%20ongoing%20war%20may%20deter%20investors%2C%20one%20expert%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20Ukraine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-signs-minerals-deal-for-access-to-ukraine-natural-resources-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%20a%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20granting%20US%20companies%20access%20to%20critical%20minerals%20like%20graphite%20and%20lithium%20in%20the%20war-torn%20country.%20But%20industry%20watchers%20say%20the%20deal's%20impact%20will%20be%20slow%20and%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20signed%20deal%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-statement-minerals-deal-trump-zelenskyy-oval-office-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoften-fraught%20negotiations%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20%E2%80%94%20gives%20US%20companies%20access%20to%20Ukraine's%20reserves%20of%20critical%20natural%20resources%20as%20part%20of%20a%20planned%20reconstruction%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20aims%2C%20in%20part%2C%20to%20diversify%20supply%20chains%20and%20support%20US%20firms%20producing%20goods%20like%20solar%20panels%20and%20EV%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Trump%20has%20said%20that%20the%20minerals%20deal%20with%20Ukraine%20could%20net%20the%20US%20%24500%20billion%20from%20rare%20earths%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20experts%20say%20the%20deal%20is%20more%20symbolic%20than%20practical%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20now%20%E2%80%94%20due%20to%20security%2C%20investment%2C%20and%20logistical%20hurdles%20that%20dampen%20expectations%20for%20any%20near-term%20payoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETimothy%20Puko%2C%20director%20of%20corporate%20commodities%20at%20the%20Eurasia%20Group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20any%20commercial%20outcomes%20from%20the%20deal%20are%20%26quot%3Bseverely%20limited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20almost%20entirely%20about%20politics%20and%20keeping%20Washington%20interested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20very%20little%20there%20to%20lure%20in%20serious%20investment%20or%20production%20that%20could%20materially%20bolster%20supply%20chains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECullen%20Hendrix%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Peterson%20Institute%20for%20International%20Economics%2C%20said%20the%20deal%20is%20%26quot%3Bmore%20smoke%20than%20fire%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20reshaping%20US%20critical%20mineral%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20Ukraine%20with%20an%20important%20lifeline%20and%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20shields%20them%20from%20a%20mountain%20of%20post-conflict%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261676c19-1bd2-4ff3-a49c-e88931c0f158%5C%22%3ETransactional%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Ukraine%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20of%20rising%20supply-chain%20uncertainty%2C%20amid%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-weigh-who-has-upper-hand-us-china-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%20US%20trade%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20China%20from%20which%2090%25%20of%20the%20world's%20rare%20earth%20metals%20are%20sourced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20uncertainties%20over%20the%20available%20resources%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErik%20Jonsson%2C%20a%20senior%20geologist%20at%20the%20Geological%20Survey%20of%20Sweden%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20March%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ukraine-mineral-rare-earth-deal-makes-little-sense-experts-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20has%20a%20solid%20mining%20industry%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20based%20on%20rare%20earths.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20agreement%20gives%20the%20current%20administration%20political%20cover%20to%20continue%20backing%20Ukraine%2C%20Hendrix%20emphasized%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20markedly%20change%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20mineral%20security%20landscape%20in%20the%20short%20or%20medium%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Young%2C%20geo-technology%20director%20at%20the%20Eurasia%20Group%2C%20said%20that%20while%20Ukraine%20holds%20large%20deposits%20of%20critical%20minerals%2C%20there's%20nothing%20particularly%20distinctive%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20question%20of%20extraction%E2%80%94and%20even%20more%20importantly%2C%20processing%20and%20refining%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BTo%20extract%2C%20you%20need%20capital%2C%20permits%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20a%20workforce%20to%20mine%20the%20raw%20ore%20profitably.%20And%20even%20then%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20to%20transport%20and%20process%20that%20ore%20may%20not%20be%20in%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20constraints%20are%20compounded%20by%20volatile%20mineral%20prices%20and%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions%2C%20particularly%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHendrix%20also%20cautioned%20against%20the%20assumption%20that%20identified%20resources%20will%20translate%20easily%20into%20viable%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAsk%20anyone%20in%20mining%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BLots%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%20logistics%2C%20prices%2C%20capital%20expenditures%E2%80%94can%20stall%20or%20kill%20projects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22918715d3-29b6-48e0-a195-caeb6d294e21%5C%22%3ELong%20lead%20times%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Michot%20Foss%2C%20a%20minerals%20expert%20at%20Rice%20University's%20Baker%20Institute%20for%20Public%20Policy%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20without%20serious%20investment%20in%20extraction%20and%20processing%2C%20resources%20will%20remain%20untapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20called%20the%20new%20deal%20a%20%26quot%3Blong-lead-time%20deal%26quot%3B%20fraught%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20multitude%20of%20risks%20and%20uncertainties%20that%20investors%20and%20policymakers%20will%20face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Foss%20pointed%20to%20past%20disappointments%20as%20a%20cautionary%20tale%20for%20those%20looking%20to%20get%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20promoted%20their%20shale%20plays%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20companies%20positioned%20with%20licenses%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Chevron%20and%20Shell's%20shale%20gas%20projects%20launched%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20lackluster%20drilling%20results%20and%20political%20instability%20halted%20both%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20said%20that%20permitting%20is%20the%20biggest%20bottleneck%20for%20most%20mining%20companies%2C%20and%20even%20if%20Ukraine%20could%20fast-track%20approvals%2C%20the%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Russia%20could%20deter%20investors%20who%20operate%20on%20multi-decade%20timelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mismatch%20in%20timing%20and%20the%20volatile%20geopolitical%20environment%20will%20likely%