0of%20batteries%2C%20whether%20they%20use%20advanced%20communication%20systems%20like%20Controller%20Area%20Network%20(CAN)%20or%20not%2C%20and%20can%20test%20batteries%20up%20to%20100%20volts%20and%20100%20ampere-hours%20in%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBattery%20tests%20that%20take%20minutes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20a%20user%20has%20to%20do%20is%20connect%20the%20device%20to%20a%20battery%20and%20charger.%20It%20then%20transmits%20real-time%20data%20%E2%80%93%20like%20voltage%2C%20current%2C%20and%20time%2C%20to%20cloud-based%20algorithms%20that%20compute%20safety%20parameters%2C%20fault%20detection%2C%20and%20capacity%20degradation.%20The%20results%20are%20sent%20back%20to%20a%20mobile%20app%20with%20a%20complete%20report%20on%20the%20battery%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20safety%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20faults%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20EV%20Doctor%20device%20has%20been%20tested%20on%20over%20five%20lakh%20batteries%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424405%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20EV%20Doctor%20device%20has%20been%20tested%20on%20over%20five%20lakh%20batteries%20so%20far%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20claim%20that%20the%20results%20have%20an%20accuracy%20of%20over%2096.7%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20tested%20it%20on%20over%20five%20lakh%20batteries%20so%20far%2C%20and%20it%20has%20helped%20prevent%20serious%20issues%2C%20including%20potential%20fire%20hazards%2C%20in%20countless%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ajay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20year%2C%20BatteryOk%20sold%20just%2020%20units%20of%C2%A0%20EV%20Doctor.%20But%20as%20word%20spread%2C%20the%20numbers%20climbed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20they%20sold%20150%20units.%20In%202024%2C%20that%20number%20reached%20500.%20By%20April%202025%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20600%20units%2C%20bringing%20their%20total%20to%20over%201%2C500%20devices%20sold%20worldwide.%20With%20a%20manufacturing%20capacity%20exceeding%201%2C000%20units%20per%20month%2C%20the%20company%20is%20expanding%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20EV%20Doctor%20is%20used%20in%20more%20than%201%2C700%20EV%20workshops%20and%20service%20centres%20across%20India%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Mauritius%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States.%20Their%20client%20list%20includes%20industry%20leaders%20such%20as%20MG%20Motors%2C%20Zypp%20Electric%2C%20Yulu%2C%20White%20Carbon%2C%20Jitendra%20EV%2C%20and%20JioBP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20someone%20running%20an%20EV%20workshop%2C%20this%20device%20has%20been%20helpful%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pawan%20Prajapat%20(34)%2C%20owner%20of%20Udaipur%20Ewheels%2C%20who%20purchased%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20could%20barely%20manage%20to%20test%20two%20or%20three%20batteries%20a%20day.%20Now%2C%20I%20test%20about%C2%A0%2010%20to%2015%20without%20breaking%20a%20sweat.%20The%20process%20is%20smooth%2C%20fast%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20gives%20me%20detailed%20insights%20without%20even%20having%20to%20open%20the%20battery%20pack.%20That%2C%20to%20me%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20relief.%20I%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%20inside%20the%20battery%20just%20by%20plugging%20it%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20full%20body%20check-up%2C%20but%20for%20batteries.%20It%20does%20not%20just%20show%20if%20something%20is%20wrong%2C%20it%20gives%20clarity%20on%20health%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20potential%20risks.%20That%20allows%20us%20to%20take%20preventive%20steps%20before%20anything%20serious%20happens.%20By%20using%20EV%20Doctor%2C%20I%20have%20tested%20hundreds%20of%20batteries%2C%20and%20not%20a%20single%20one%20has%20led%20to%20thermal%20issues.%20That%20alone%20has%20probably%20saved%20us%20lakhs%20in%20potential%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20workshop%20owner%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-1746030410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20has%20sold%20600%20units%20of%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20so%20far%20in%202025%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-174603041