Then%20came%20the%20moment%20that%20changed%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%202%20January%202020.%20I%20was%20taking%20a%20bath%20and%20looking%20out%20of%20the%20window%20at%20the%20coconut%20trees%20around%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Suddenly%2C%20a%20visual%20flashed%20in%20his%20mind%3A%20a%20futuristic%20robot%20climbing%20up%20a%20tree%20and%20harvesting%20coconuts.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20decided%20this%20would%20be%20my%20next%20big%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanting%20the%20seeds%20for%20Coco-bot%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshin%20spent%20the%20next%20year%20immersed%20in%20deep%20research%20and%20development.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20look%20up%20existing%20prototypes%20or%20models%20online.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20how%20Coco-bot%20should%20be.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20influenced%20by%20what%20was%20already%20out%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202021%2C%20he%20had%20built%20a%20low-quality%20prototype%20but%20got%20caught%20up%20with%20college%20work%20after%20enrolling%20for%20a%20diploma%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20at%20JDT%20Engineering%20College.%20Still%2C%20the%20dream%20of%20building%20Coco-bot%20never%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Ashin%20participated%20in%20the%2036-hour-long%20Vaiga%20Agri%20Hackathon%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20Kerala.%20Coco-bot%20went%20on%20to%20win%20the%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20a%20turning%20point%20that%20brought%20his%20work%20into%20the%20spotlight.%20Soon%20after%2C%20NABARD%20(National%20Bank%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20Rural%20Development)%20rea